name: Sinseoldong Nights
description: Sinseoldong is one of the areas nearest to my home. I have spent countless hours exploring and taking pictures here, yet it seems every time I go out to take photos, I come back with a lovely photograph. One of the things that sets this photograph apart from my other pieces is that I do not usually photograph traffic or intersections, I never really liked that. But on this particular night, I really liked the way the street, the scene, the people, and the rain came together.
